{"tid":2399910,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英領館：獲悉香港不承認雙重國籍 持英護照入境未必能獲領事協助","createTime":"2021-02-08T13:24:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T03:52:38.000Z","uid":53844,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c808103a03ddcea183aa5f903caf79e7d1ad4306","tid":2399910,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:24:10.000Z","msg":"英國政府早前開放港人申請BNO特別簽證，隨即引來中港兩地反制，更有傳中國政府有意在港引入《國籍法》，不容許香港人持有雙重國籍。<br />\n<br />\n繼加拿大外交部日前指，香港拒絕領事館為雙重國籍被拘人士提供協助後，英國駐港總領事館今（8日）稱，獲悉香港不承認雙重國籍，擁有雙重國籍人士在港，即使持英國護照入境，都可能未能獲得領事協助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210208/PPXF6Y5RV5CRXK4KOIFQ7ALBCY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210208%2FPPXF6Y5RV5CRXK4KOIFQ7ALBCY%2F&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUipq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=41ecf7b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210208%2FPPXF6Y5RV5CRXK4KOIFQ7ALBCY%2F&h=7aade0de\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210208/PPXF6Y5RV5CRXK4KOIFQ7ALBCY/</a>"},{"pid":"49a716dc43e8bab4100bf0d6a971473f243f5eff","tid":2399910,"uid":64345,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:25:22.000Z","msg":"被中國籍"},{"pid":"a57de0f123c841e59091fd68da2cb84ef924d57b","tid":2399910,"uid":255045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf390b814ae2e50eea32e537a6672322e328f27","tid":2399910,"uid":33556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419f125e482c6a528a81ccd9ea37d820618d71be","tid":2399910,"uid":115608,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:29:47.000Z","msg":"首先係中國人<br />\n<br />\n就算國籍變更，要捉你嘅下場將會同瑞典籍嘅桂民海一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ccc8b70b2da40033909600da24412031e1c806","tid":2399910,"uid":19165,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:30:27.000Z","msg":"學訓街卿話齋, 最撚恐怖係由英國政府同加拿大政府幫你宣佈中止雙重國藉政策, 佢自己都唔敢行出黎講"},{"pid":"50ede5933d8b17fd7062af47ee01461a926596f7","tid":2399910,"uid":266654,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:30:56.000Z","msg":"即係提水叫你班BNO快D走，而家支那夾鳩硬黎，只要你係中國人樣＋中國名＋係香港，英國就唔可以提供領使服務。<br />\n包括BNO ／BC ／加拿大籍......."},{"pid":"63e67b20d137218d9b9d0f9f4176c785137416f8","tid":2399910,"uid":33028,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"38ccc8b70b2da40033909600da24412031e1c806","tid":2399910,"uid":19165,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:30:27.000Z","msg":"學訓街卿話齋, 最撚恐怖係由英國政府同加拿大政府幫你宣佈中止雙重國藉政策, 佢自己都唔敢行出黎講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:32:13.000Z","msg":"一早寫明，唔係今日先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全國人民代表大會常務委員會關於《中華人民共和國國籍法》在香港特別行政區實施的幾個問題的解釋<br />\n四. 在外國有居留權的香港特別行政區的中國公民，可使用外國政府簽發的有關證件去其他國家或地區旅行，但在香港特別行政區和中華人民共和國其他地區不得因持有上述證件而享有外國領事保護的權利。"},{"pid":"d32413447e5069069a5a3f235984e820908bd404","tid":2399910,"uid":254742,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:35:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1afe436b11e5a4db574350140dcd1d7dcc737899","tid":2399910,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:37:31.000Z","msg":"屌，唔承認咋？<br />\n幾時先褫奪BNO嘅中國籍先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0068d78c6dbbf5a770b96622ef5094df3d3f0da","tid":2399910,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T16:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41f11a9f0f03dd27ea03108f05baa7addf3f2a97","tid":2399910,"uid":389613,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T16:44:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/uk-51306996\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fuk-51306996&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUipq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=c87603e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fuk-51306996&h=469e89c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/uk-51306996</a><br />\n<br />\n中國不承認雙重國籍，但英國允許雙重國籍的存在。<span class=\"red\">中國不允許雙重國籍護照持有人通過撤僑通道離開中國。</span><br />\n<br />\n來自約克的弗朗西斯（Natalie Francis）說，<span class=\"red\">她被告知必須將三歲的兒子留在中國，因為兒子有中國護照。</span><br />\n<br />\n她說：「接到電話時，我無語了。」"},{"pid":"725f8a048fa9787dbed59eb5bd0e48406a883dc7","tid":2399910,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T16:51:18.000Z","msg":"簡單講條友有回鄉証 特區護照就係中國藉男子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d5e1e16fee9eb596b23ca3afc9801e97786a55","tid":2399910,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T16:53:06.000Z","msg":"香港班BC好閉翳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3f19e3f1efd7f0d9346940635fdec737ba848c","tid":2399910,"uid":194298,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"50ede5933d8b17fd7062af47ee01461a926596f7","tid":2399910,"uid":266654,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:30:56.000Z","msg":"即係提水叫你班BNO快D走，而家支那夾鳩硬黎，只要你係中